data.description: THIS HOME HAS VAULTED CEILINGS IN THE MAIN LIVING AREAS, MASTER AND BEDROOM 2.  THERE IS LAMINATE WOOD FLOORING THROUGHOUT THE MAIN AREAS.  ALL BEDROOMS ARE OVER-SIZED.  THE MASTER BATH HAS A GARDEN TUB AND SHOWER.  BEDROOM 4 COULD BE USED AS A MOTHER-IN-LAW SUITE, AS IT HAS A FULL BATH WITH SHOWER AND JETTED TUB, AND AN OFFICE/STUDY AREA.  LARGE LAUNDRY ROOM.  OPEN KITCHEN AND BREAKFAST AREA WITH UPGRADED TRIM, SOLID WOOD CABINETS AND STAINLESS APPLIANCES.  RECENTLY PAINTED THROUGHOUT.  SELLER TO INSTALL A 12'x16' REAR DECK FOR BUYER PRIOR TO CLOSING.
